nodes.text: Tarand Crowe was a Human male Smuggler who was onboard the Tansarii Point Station for a period of time during the Galactic Civil War. While he was on the station, he would smuggle goods from place to place.

Tarand Crowe was a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
